# Filament Multi Auth Guard

## When to use

- Configuring multiple Filament panels with separate auth guards
- Creating separate login pages for admin, member, vendor, etc.
- Setting up multiple user tables and models with independent authentication
- Configuring password reset brokers per guard
- Implementing `FilamentUser` on custom user models

